Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.94,0:23:29.11,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,50)\blur1}INSIDE MY FEELING INSIDE MY JUSTICE　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:31.69,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,50)\blur1}邪魔しないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:31.69,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,50)\blur1}別打擾我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:33.77,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,50)\blur1}居場所はどこ!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:33.77,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,50)\blur1}歸所在哪!
